No. 619,

Misc.

Ragan v. Cox, Commandant, U. S. Disciplinary Barracks. Frederick Bernays Wiener and Robert E. Hannon for petitioner. Solicitor General Cox, Assistant Attorney General Marshall and Harold H. Greene for respondent.

C. A. 10th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
